   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:03.03" end="00:00:05.56" region="speaker">Eliminating product offerings is a necessary</p>
         <p begin="00:00:05.56" end="00:00:07.33" region="speaker">business function.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.33" end="00:00:08.90" region="speaker">Enter a detailed description of your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:08.90" end="00:00:11.40" region="speaker">request, and identify the product you would like</p>
         <p begin="00:00:11.40" end="00:00:13.53" region="speaker">removed from your schedule.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:13.53" end="00:00:16.10" region="speaker">You can also provide the CO with some information</p>
         <p begin="00:00:16.10" end="00:00:18.26" region="speaker">as to why you are removing this product from your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.26" end="00:00:19.66" region="speaker">schedule.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:19.66" end="00:00:22.23" region="speaker">Deletion modifications fall under the category</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.23" end="00:00:24.80" region="speaker">known as &quot;Rapid Action Modifications&quot;.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:24.80" end="00:00:27.00" region="speaker">This means that a contractor can submit a</p>
         <p begin="00:00:27.00" end="00:00:29.46" region="speaker">Deletion Modification request and the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:29.46" end="00:00:31.90" region="speaker">Contracting Officer can approve it without having</p>
         <p begin="00:00:31.90" end="00:00:34.46" region="speaker">to go through the signature process.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:34.46" end="00:00:36.20" region="speaker">When you are finished click &quot;Save and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:36.20" end="00:00:38.16" region="speaker">continue.&quot;</p>
    </div>
